The first basic version of ALPHA was written by

- Johannes Gilger <Johannes.Gilger@RWTH-Aachen.de>
- Florian Weingarten <Florian.Weingarten@RWTH-Aachen.de>

during "Mobile Communication Systems Engineering Lab" in winter term 2008/2009
at RWTH-Aachen University (Distributed Systems Group).

During summer term 2009, the following people also worked intensively on ALPHA,
especially on ALPHA C and ALPHA M:

- Christian Dernehl <Christian.Dernehl@RWTH-Aachen.de>
- Tobias Heer <Tobias.Heer@CS.RWTH-Aachen.de>

